    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the styles of a disparate group of landscape painters active from the early 1880s in and around the town of Newlyn, in Cornwall. The artists in the group, such as Stanhope Forbes, Walter Langley, and Frank Bramleyl, were known to continue the French naturalist and English Pre-Raphaelite traditions in their work. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079228/Grove Art Online (2008-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000047294/Tate [online] (2005-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指1880年代初期活躍於康瓦耳紐林一帶的許多風景畫家之繪畫風格。包括斯坦厄普．福布斯、華特．藍利與法蘭克．布侖里等隸屬此團體的畫家，在其畫風上仍延續法國自然主義和英國前拉斐爾派傳統。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052784/TELDAP database (2009-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Verwijst naar de stijlen van een diverse groep landschapsschilders die vanaf het begin van de jaren tachtig van de 19e eeuw actief waren in en rond de stad Newlyn in Cornwall. De kunstenaars in de groep - onder wie Stanhope Forbes, Walter Langley en Frank Bramleyl - volgden de Frans naturalistische en Engels prerafaëlitische tradities. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
